ticker-image\" />\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-59408e6f-a219-4562-af9e-1f63c5055215\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-00e17b5f-cd52-4085-81f9-9afec30b0459\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-aaee101b-10a4-4c18-9ca3-5894beefb455\"><b>아이의 비만, 단순히 살만 찌는 문제가 아닙니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0b6ee6f5-20cd-42d8-8e5e-2f65301857a2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0304dea9-5caf-4dff-bc72-249da7f638c1\">어릴 때 시작된 비만은 80% 이상이 성인 비만으로 이어지며, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2f1b645e-ce29-4d19-b25c-64873bbf7327\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-52f6b2da-3a7d-43a2-a84b-4936b0a437c2\">당뇨·고혈압·지방간 같은 성인병의 위험을 높입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7f382116-750b-4728-bc95-f0c3b65a159e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-775f7216-3a99-46b5-b6c2-f68fc6546074\">성장기 건강을 해치는 중요한 원인이 될 수 있기에 조기 관리가 필수적입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-59408e6f-a219-4562-af9e-1f63c5055215\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-ef2978bb-b5c9-4827-aca2-14bd7afece4b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-center\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-12c86ac5-66cd-4943-b1ed-25770f972daa\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-12c86ac5-66cd-4943-b1ed-25770f972daa\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/05f50e6eb174c90e.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"800\", \"originalHeight\" : \"800\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/05f50e6eb174c90e.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/05f50e6eb174c90e.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-12c86ac5-66cd-4943-b1ed-25770f972daa\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9d3ef8dc-b828-410f-ab8e-2dd0fd0688bb\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-default\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2b0910ae-3bb5-47bf-a529-8ba24e7a9fb2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-75e12ac9-93cf-4ab3-8d3d-a75e4a70292f\">소아비만이 성인비만으로 이어지는 이유</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ff6997f4-ee6d-4b94-8498-bf2f2febb861\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8843e0b1-8f47-4e2f-b8d5-fb04a9f4dec2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ef0d6e02-f72d-4ebd-89d1-a2c14cd0ef1e\">아이의 체지방 세포는 성장기에 급격히 늘어나고 쉽게 줄어들지 않습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-02871064-aaf7-4888-9c0e-1d00202714c3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-57c38090-25cf-49b6-8158-a34afc93be1c\">따라서 어릴 때 과체중을 겪으면 지방 세포 수 자체가 많아져 성인이 되어도 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6d023e3c-cbdb-43e3-b9b0-e0b6de11398c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-230fc340-118f-4ef0-bab9-835e44a8f10b\">쉽게 살이 빠지지 않고 비만으로 고착될 위험이 큽니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-ff6997f4-ee6d-4b94-8498-bf2f2febb861\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-763e7703-28f5-4c47-875c-ed3939e9282f\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-center\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-96a94a38-d6bd-41d4-ba51-3914550791a7\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-098e275c-7735-482e-9be6-5521b8a326fc\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f82dcccc-cb7b-4922-a649-12cceebd0b2e\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-96a94a38-d6bd-41d4-ba51-3914550791a7\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-a7a38a34-8549-43b6-a27a-d8d7efc6f079\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-18369936-237c-4325-bf4e-ee4f73a6b9e9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-01360ba5-8d0a-4422-a5df-4be33ae521e9\"><b>성장판에도 영향을 주는 비만</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-238c838f-687b-469a-87bb-5faf0d02b565\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9b5ce8c0-fccd-4a44-b3f1-001b3d8a369c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c2076e9b-9605-4592-80bc-188f4909ee70\">비만은 단순히 체중 문제에 그치지 않고 성장판 발달에 영향을 줍니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d78262c6-a8e9-4e91-baa1-e62b12df2123\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b0fc307d-305a-4207-87ac-9d4e2272805b\">체중 부담으로 인해 성장판이 손상되면 키 성장이 더디게 되거나, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-456f0399-9291-47e6-a1b9-afbeabe36d1b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3b18f966-e176-47d2-9644-8024e672ceff\">예상보다 키가 크지 못하는 결과를 초래할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c7faeaf8-6e65-4dec-87d1-396ce32a213a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4e28ac8e-9b70-4e93-8c97-d06e5569a9ba\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-238c838f-687b-469a-87bb-5faf0d02b565\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-45f4d633-87bb-4782-a93b-2a8d47e8b1f4\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-49cf114d-3fd8-4903-b15e-09f5fc978b9a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4c851aba-1fce-4e64-b356-30beed33527f\"><b>인스턴트·패스트푸드의 위험성</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-149fb546-c098-4256-9deb-b6565e3d2993\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-99dc7476-d431-4f3b-a04b-1cd56f80723d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e28c3f54-9150-40ae-adf8-7ffd6949c7b2\">햄버거, 치킨, 피자 등 인스턴트·패스트푸드 위주의 식단은 열량은 높고 영양소는 불균형합니다. 이런 식습관은 체지방 축적을 빠르게 만들고, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a2656bed-f12a-4ad5-ba0f-8f44deb6dcc8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-446b3c37-f4fa-4fdb-8aa3-a94a524dd0ca\">혈당·혈압 조절에도 악영향을 주어 성인병 위험을 크게 높입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6fc9b83f-e551-47ad-b726-b6da2cf7c9ee\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-dd938709-2383-47fc-a71d-186ebf55573b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-149fb546-c098-4256-9deb-b6565e3d2993\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-9574d646-3b89-4cf7-a3e6-aaba265f6406\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1c4b3db3-f802-4bd7-b7ef-397f3b67df8d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-181d4a65-ff51-4db2-b1c4-e99797ebd3ea\"><b>아이 비만을 막는 7가지 생활 습관</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-95c62379-77cd-49a7-ac5b-fc0b44ea404c\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9d0ade45-4518-45a0-82ee-20b6452a72f0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8f8e5b5c-cdac-464d-9df5-57669bae1d06\">규칙적인 세 끼 식사 유지</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4af12c52-89c3-4987-a604-afa1995d117d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a45444a6-a0de-4bac-810f-3b1f44f5d0ce\">채소와 단백질 위주의 균형 잡힌 식단</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d54eb05e-8485-4b0f-8cab-07f48137a556\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-31c82f20-7f66-436a-869f-8dfa29b73e9f\">가공식품·단 음료 줄이기</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f2434626-83fb-4bde-8d7a-a0437db6a15c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-49d6ed80-3c66-4e8e-8f97-5d4776a37550\">하루 30분 이상 유산소 운동</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7f1b11f8-a92f-4afb-b65f-3e4bbca57ba0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7bd7bf5b-5203-494b-96c1-92da962952e2\">TV·스마트폰 사용 시간 줄이기</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-053ea4c9-9be6-4836-9511-86dfdc8dd9da\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e5f89cf9-d2a5-4818-bbe9-878ba3112221\">충분한 수면 확보</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-420d8de9-7981-4ee9-826b-ddf330d025ef\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1ab5f403-35fc-4119-b5a0-21a4c3a32739\">부모와 함께하는 건강한 생활 습관 형성</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-84114ffd-66b8-42dd-8569-823294abe871\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bc387c7c-c4af-40df-b409-5453eb93c6e6\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-95c62379-77cd-49a7-ac5b-fc0b44ea404c\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5a27fb1b-15fe-46ce-ba6c-2db56096da3e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-5a27fb1b-15fe-46ce-ba6c-2db56096da3e\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/eaa7e2660c3e6a45.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1024\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1112\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/eaa7e2660c3e6a45.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2